  "detailed_description": "<strong>Glorious Tournius Mode</strong>  2-4 Players - Are you ready to fight in the Glorious Tournius? Experience active ragdoll, physics based mayhem in this local multiplayer game. Battle each other using bombs, guns, melee weapons and your fists.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401890/extras/3c6344c57e7376f7377d82f3e6836b8f.poster.avif?t=1619823234\" width=800 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401890/extras/3c6344c57e7376f7377d82f3e6836b8f.webm?t=1619823234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401890/extras/3c6344c57e7376f7377d82f3e6836b8f.mp4?t=1619823234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Zombie Mode</strong>  1-4 Players - How long can you survive against endless waves of the undead?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401890/extras/b4591cada09d66eb88d881e57e4cbd7c.poster.avif?t=1619823234\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401890/extras/b4591cada09d66eb88d881e57e4cbd7c.webm?t=1619823234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401890/extras/b4591cada09d66eb88d881e57e4cbd7c.mp4?t=1619823234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Bombs</strong>  A range of bombs, including ice, sticky and landmines<br><br><strong>Physics Weapons</strong>  Unique weapons that can slow down your opponents <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401890/extra